Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黄色意味着温度较高\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yellow means warmer temperatures
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高于1880年代任何地区的平均水平\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than the average, for any region in the 1880s.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}橙色意味着炎热\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Orange means hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:40.99,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}红色意味着比炎热更热\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And red means hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:44.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界已经变得比19世纪更温暖了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The world is warmer than it was in the 19th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:51.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时 全球各地的气温是有史以来最均衡的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Back then, at the greatest fair the world has ever seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:56.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一位被遗忘的天才曾设想了一个解决问题的方案\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a forgotten genius demonstrated the solution to this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾经有这样一个世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once there was a world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它不太热也不太冷\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that was not too hot and not too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温度适中\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后有一天 这里的人们\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then there came a time when the life it sustained
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:21.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始注意到他们可爱的地球在发生变化\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}began to notice our lovely planet was changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:25.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这并不是说我们没有预见到它的到来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's not as if we didn't see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:36.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三十一. 关于碳酸空气中对地面温度的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早在1896年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As far back as 1896,
