Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通过计算发现 如果大气中的二氧化碳含量再增加1倍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}calculated that doubling the amount
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:42.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}大气就如温室一般
