Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了1930年代 美国物理学家E.O.赫尔伯特\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the 1930s, the American physicist E. O. Hulburt,
