Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确认了这个结果\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}confirmed that result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:53.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}二氧化碳令地球变热
