Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.38,0:35:52.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在大约1万年前 我们在世界各地的祖先\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}About 10,000 years ago, our ancestors all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.05,0:35:55.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利用了另一种形式的气候突变\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}took advantage of another form of climate change,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.62,0:35:59.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冰河时代间歇期中出现的温和天气\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the gentler climate of the intermission in the ice age--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.89,0:36:03.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们发明了农业\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they invented agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.46,0:36:05.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们放弃了无休止的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They gave up the ceaseless wandering,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.63,0:36:08.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}流浪 游猎以及采集的生活方式\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hunting and gathering that had been their way of life
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.93,0:36:10.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种方式曾延续了1百万年之久\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for a million years or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.93,0:36:14.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们定居下来 生产食物\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to settle down and produce food.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.54,0:36:17.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们发现耕作农田\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They found a way to harvest
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.06,0:36:19.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能让他们比先人通过自然环境\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ten to a hundred times more solar energy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.96,0:36:24.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}获得要高出十到百倍之多的太阳能\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than the environment naturally provided for their ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.76,0:36:28.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界各地的人们艰难地实现了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People all over the world made the difficult transition
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.30,0:36:31.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从游牧文化向农耕文化的转变\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from nomadic cultures to agricultural ones
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:34.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是一种更有效的使用太阳能的方式\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that used solar energy more efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.84,0:36:38.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这让文明兴盛起来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It gave rise to civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:42.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们就站在那些辛勤劳作的先人的肩上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We stand on the shoulders of those who did the hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.05,0:36:45.62,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们为我们实现最基础的转变\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that such a fundamental transformation required.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.65,0:36:49.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 该轮到我们了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now... it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.89,0:36:56.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾经有这样一个世界……\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once there was a world...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.30,0:37:05.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果在金星上曾有过生命 他们也不会有机会\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If life ever existed on Venus, it would have had no chance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.24,0:37:08.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扭转这个世界走向地狱的命运\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to avert the hellish destiny of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.48,0:37:14.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种失控的温室效应是无法阻挡的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This runaway greenhouse effect was unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:25.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾经\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.26,0:37:27.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有这样一个世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there was a world...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.47,0:37:31.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是我们的世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.63,0:37:34.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是现在的世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that world is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.30,0:37:36.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有任何科学或技术上的障碍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are no scientific or technological obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.81,0:37:38.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会阻止我们保护这个世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to protecting our world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.68,0:37:42.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保护这个世界上珍贵的生命\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the precious life that it supports.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.15,0:37:44.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都取决于\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It all depends...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.05,0:37:47.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们真正珍惜的是什么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on what we truly value...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.05,0:37:50.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们能否付诸于行动\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and if we can summon the will to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.33,0:38:40.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"为什么" 有人问 为什么要选择月亮\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But why, some say, the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.53,0:38:43.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么把它作为我们的目标？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why choose this as our goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.70,0:38:45.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们也许还会问\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they may well ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.84,0:38:48.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们为什么要登上世界的最高峰？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}why climb the highest mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.34,0:38:53.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我们选择了登月\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We choose to go to the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.25,0:39:01.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们选择了在十年内登月\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}...we choose to go to the Moon in this decade
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:03.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们还要做其它的事情\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and do the other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.69,0:39:07.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是因为它们很容易 而是因为它们很难\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not because they are easy, but because they are hard.
